REPORTING PROBLEMS

Use these commands:

  bug <description>     report a game bug
  idea <description>    suggest a feature
  typo <description>    report a text error

For player conduct issues, contact staff on the OOC channel with a concise
summary. Include character names, times, and what happened.

Staff review logs when available but cannot always witness private disputes.

SEE ALSO: rules, harassment, bug, idea, typo
